,"msg":"<blockquote>monorail 係廢嘅<br />\n好在無起</blockquote><br />\n睇人口黎做<br />\n如果好似江之島咁少人住就可行既"},{"pid":"05615abbc9d8ad37c6a1559a276a49f963e2511f","tid":398692,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\n你住觀塘？"},{"pid":"5779f20932906cd0309522b0e0a9984af2ae654c","tid":398692,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起咗咪等於架空嘅輕鐵，慢到死，同地鐵接唔到，又阻地方，好似新界西而家咁，好彩冇起</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當係架空電車都爽啦<br />\n銅鑼灣位電車都會塞<br />\n架空就唔駛塞"},{"pid":"8f763575a3f13be81ed57b4ceb4ebd67d11efaac","tid":398692,"uid":46013,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>起咗咪等於架空嘅輕鐵，慢到死，同地鐵接唔到，又阻地方，好似新界西而家咁，好彩冇起</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當係架空電車都爽啦<br />\n銅鑼灣位電車都會塞<br />\n架空就唔駛塞</blockquote><br />\n依家九東既環保連接系統都係MONORAIL 好似有機會通過啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1564b402f745ce2ce06df3d221213210a80328","tid":398692,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>起咗咪等於架空嘅輕鐵，慢到死，同地鐵接唔到，又阻地方，好似新界西而家咁，好彩冇起</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當係架空電車都爽啦<br />\n銅鑼灣位電車都會塞<br />\n架空就唔駛塞</blockquote><br />\n依家九東既環保連接系統都係MONORAIL 好似有機會通過啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通過好呀<br />\n地鐡點解快 巴士點解慢<br />\n主因係會塞車<br />\n交通越繁忙的地區<br />\n架空鐵路的優點就越大"},{"pid":"66357187ab3fa9823d86755a7850a69cd22fe79c","tid":398692,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>operating cost 高 載客量低<br />\n香港輕鐵都爆棚仲玩單軌<br />\n啟德嗰陣仲話起monorail<br />\n人口密度咁高根本唔岩起<br />\n人口密度低玩輕鐵仲化算<br />\n<br />\n有d monorail 已經拆左<br />\n有d 起起下決定止蝕<br />\n有d 胎死腹中<br />\n有d 長期蝕</blockquote><br />\n冇錯<br />\n有玩過city skyline 就會明要起條咁嘅嘢係完全唔符合經濟效益</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb52a7a7fa35529b805741ceef5f278bb03ca4c","tid":398692,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該共存（地鐵+單軌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腦魔係時候進修下"},{"pid":"fbbf88d268e3b5d2991d5fae5712e25a06d7492e","tid":398692,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>monorail 係廢嘅<br />\n好在無起</blockquote><br />\n睇人口黎做<br />\n如果好似江之島咁少人住就可行既</blockquote><br />\n錯, 少人低密度更加唔可行, 用架空纜車好喇 <br />\n江之島個例子係要喺山勢下preserve地面低矮建築, 日本有另一個類似系統都係用 suspended monorail 不過再小型啲, 貼近纜車/GRT/小型APM"},{"pid":"2caa6291495a3b8e6972f16f2ddbeb9c831a5a60","tid":398692,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"70年代已經有咁嘅設計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2017 都仲覺得有啲科幻"},{"pid":"61088a9a82740985b9f6fc557af418f2775905a7","tid":398692,"uid":48835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"好彩冇起,起左仲塞過呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9a0359cbec9f55899f57a440df5cf8982171bd","tid":398692,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>monorail 係廢嘅<br />\n好在無起</blockquote><br />\n睇人口黎做<br />\n如果好似江之島咁少人住就可行既</blockquote><br />\n錯, 少人低密度更加唔可行, 用架空纜車好喇 <br />\n江之島個例子係要喺山勢下preserve地面低矮建築, 再加上兩端有anchor夠客量夠需求, 距離夠遠 <br />\n江之電本身有諗過做呢條走廊 <br />\n日本有另一個類似系統都係用 suspended monorail 不過再小型啲, 貼近纜車/GRT/小型APM</blockquote><br />\n[edit]"},{"pid":"3604d8243fb5d824f7bb19302d74331740932995","tid":398692,"uid"